channel.title: How do i make a tree give me 20k Each time i chop a log?
channel.description: I found the tree in client.java and everything and I made it so it gives me 995 instead of the magic log ID. How do i make it give me 995 20000 each time?

item.title: How do i make a tree give me 20k Each time i chop a log?
item.dc:creator: @primadude Primadude
item.description:
@primadude wrote:

Where you changed the log ID, to 995, you’ll have to change the value next to it. It’ll look something like this:

addItem(995, 1);

Change the “1” to 20000.
